data.description: Welcome to this beautiful one owner home that has been meticulously cared for and is move in ready for its new family to make lasting memories in. This exquisite property features 2862 sq ft, 4 bedrooms plus a den/office, and 3 full bathrooms, complemented by a spacious 3 car garage. The entire exterior (2020) and interior (2023) of the home has been freshly painted. Step inside the covered brick paved front porch with NEWER (2020) solid wood double doors to discover the modern elegance of BRAND NEW WATERPROOF LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING seamlessly flowing throughout the home, complemented by BRAND NEW PLUSH BEIGE CARPETING in all 4 bedrooms. The living room, dining room, family room and kitchen are open concept which allow plenty of room for gathering family and friends together. The kitchen has solid stone countertops, wood cabinets, and has been updated with ALL BRAND NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES and FAUCET, including a natural gas stove cooktop which you will love. It also offers TWO pantry's and a spacious eating area surrounded by windows looking out to the peaceful Lanai. The family room has a custom shiplap wall and sliding doors to the enclosed Lanai overlooking the gorgeous in-ground pool. The primary bedroom is enormous and offers lots of light and tranquility with sliding doors to the pool, and TWO closets (one Walk-in) with an abundance of storage. The primary ensuite bathroom has brand new faucets, dual sinks, brand new toilet, walk-in shower and a magnificent soaking tub. Bedrooms #2, #3 and #4 have spacious closets and are all on one side of the home which easily can share the two full bathrooms, one with a tub, one with a walk-in shower, and both with brand new faucets and toilets. This conveniently split floor plan allows you to entertain house guests while still maintaining your privacy. The Laundry Room has a deep sink plus a closet and cabinets which provide extra storage. The Den/Office is in the rear of the home with sliding doors to the lanai which provides a quiet and pleasant working space. Find a backyard oasis with a generously sized pool with a water fall feature which creates a soothing and serene atmosphere. The lanai has been freshly repainted, providing an ideal space for outdoor relaxation, especially with preserve views which give you total privacy. Start enjoying the fabulous lifestyle that Florida has to offer. Behind the wrought iron gates of River Place is a wonderful place to live where you will find a newly remodeled clubhouse and pool, gym, playground, picturesque streets, trails and a kayak launch to the Manatee River! Fantastic schools, lots of restaurants and shopping close by, and close proximity to I75 which makes it an easy commute to Lakewood Ranch, Sarasota, St. Pete, Tampa and our amazing beaches. Low HOA fees, and NO CDD make this home a MUST SEE! Both HVACS are only 3 years old and the roof is in great condition. What are you waiting for? Schedule your showing today and experience the allure of River Place for yourself!
